review_title: after a week 4 tyres replaced for elantra 2015
review_comment: the negative of ordering these is that they take upto a week to come also sometimes the quantity allowance is 1 2 units besides i ordered 2 tyres first when they came got them installed on the rear wheels of my elantra 2015 then i ordered two more that arrived a week later i got them installed yesterday here is something i have noticed a my original tyres ran 58000 kms but braking slipping driving and grip was an issue i get my car regularly serviced but the technicians always say change tyres as wheel alignment not possible or useless with old tyres b after replacing just 2 tyres in the rear i noticed a difference but the real difference i noticed after installing all four tyres now the car is quieter smoother seems have to better suspension grip c spending rs 24000 and it feels like i have a new car really this i should have done much before d before changing tyres i got my car serviced so that is also boosting its moving speed and fluidity but the tyres are a gamechanger i find the tyres not to be too expensive the reason i did not go for tyres that cost much less is because i have heard cheap tyres are smaller in height and may impact the height of the car ceat has impressed me so far the old tyres i have kept in my office and hope to get 3000 for all of them don t keep old tyres in your trunk as the sound will be unpleasant when you drive my old goodyear tyres had a fifth wheel that i used only 3 times in 7 years so i am happy buy without fear thanks

review_title: after a week 4 tyres replaced for elantra 2015
review_comment: the negative of ordering these is that they take upto a week to come also sometimes the quantity allowance is 1 2 units besides i ordered 2 tyres first when they came got them installed on the rear wheels of my elantra 2015 then i ordered two more that arrived a week later i got them installed yesterday here is something i have noticed a my original tyres ran 58000 kms but braking slipping driving and grip was an issue i get my car regularly serviced but the technicians always say change tyres as wheel alignment not possible or useless with old tyres b after replacing just 2 tyres in the rear i noticed a difference but the real difference i noticed after installing all four tyres now the car is quieter smoother seems have to better suspension grip c spending rs 24000 and it feels like i have a new car really this i should have done much before d before changing tyres i got my car serviced so that is also boosting its moving speed and fluidity but the tyres are a gamechanger i find the tyres not to be too expensive the reason i did not go for tyres that cost much less is because i have heard cheap tyres are smaller in height and may impact the height of the car ceat has impressed me so far the old tyres i have kept in my office and hope to get 3000 for all of them don t keep old tyres in your trunk as the sound will be unpleasant when you drive my old goodyear tyres had a fifth wheel that i used only 3 times in 7 years so i am happy buy without fear thanks
